        <section id="about" class="content">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
                        <div class="image-wrapper landscape fadein">
                            <div class="image">
                                <img class="placeholder" src="{{ 'about-1.jpg' | asset_url }}" onload="setAsBackground(this);"/>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xs-7 col-xs-offset-5 col-md-7 col-md-offset-5">
                        <h3>Sustainable</h3>
                        <p>Horn is a totally sustainable and natural material. The fibre of horn carries with it properties that outweigh any synthetic counterpart. Lightweight and durable, each pair will gracefully flex and gradually mould to the contours of the wearer’s face.</p>
                        <h3>1/1</h3>
                        <p>Horn is a natural fibre; its integrity, pattern and structure cannot be replicated, making each individual pair of Lewis Fredericks a completely unique, one of a kind piece.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xs-7 col-md-7">
                        <div class="image-wrapper portrait fadein">
                            <div class="image">
                                <img class="placeholder" src="{{ 'about-2.jpg' | asset_url }}" onload="setAsBackground(this);"/>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xs-7 col-xs-offset-5 col-md-7 col-md-offset-5">
                        <h3>Handmade</h3>
                        <p>With mass production and little technique now a calling card of the eyewear industry, Lewis Fredericks instead pays tribute to the rich history of eyewear’s past, through recycling the traditionally used material of horn, polarised lenses and expert hand craftsmanship.</p>
                        <h3>Ethical</h3>
                        <p>Lewis Fredericks Eyewear offers time-honoured silhouettes fashioned from waste horn, the previously discarded by-product of domesticated Buffalo, Ox and Ram.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
                        <div class="image-wrapper landscape fadein">
                            <div class="image">
                                <img class="placeholder" src="{{ 'about-3.jpg' | asset_url }}" onload="setAsBackground(this);"/>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
